OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloud increasing from the
OL,6,Fnorthwest this morning, with some
OL,7,Fpatchy light rain arriving later. This
OL,8,Fclearing to sunny spells and perhaps
OL,9,Fthe odd shower during the afternoon.
OL,10,FBecoming breezy, and feeling cold for
OL,11,Fthe time of year.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAny showers fading during the
OL,14,Fevening, with clear skies developing
OL,15,Ffor a time. However, further showers
OL,16,Fwill arrive across the region during
OL,17,Fthe overnight period, these heavy and
OL,18,Fblustery later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
