OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FA day of sunny spells and
OL,6,Fblustery showers, some of the showers
OL,7,Flocally heavy with hail and thunder.
OL,8,FFeeling rather cold with temperatures
OL,9,Fbelow normal.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,12,FFurther heavy showers likely on
OL,13,FThursday and perhaps Friday, which
OL,14,Falso carry a risk of thunder. Some
OL,15,Fsunny spells in the mix too. Drier and
OL,16,Fbrighter on Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
